Shirye-shiryen manyan kantunan Sainsbury's sun shiga kasuwar kayan kwalliya ta Burtaniya
Babban kantin sayar da kayayyaki na Sainsbury's ya shiga cikin Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams kuma yanzu yana ba da sassan kayan ado na salon manyan kantuna tare da ma'aikata masu ƙwarewa da ƙwarewa.
