A halin yanzu, Livingston ta ci gaba da kasancewa ba a doke ta ba kuma akwai wasanni shida a wannan kakar, kuma kocin Holt bai san abin da rashin nasara yake nufi ba tun lokacin da ya maye gurbin Kenny Miller a watan da ya gabata.
