Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin samun damar samun ilimi ne ke sa matasa shiga cikin 'yan bindiga.
Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take bai wa AA.
A cewar mai saka jari Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple, da kuma masanin AI, "Yin aiki da kasar Sin a kan fasaha ta wucin gadi zai sa Amurka ta ninka yawan kudaden da take kashewa a kan wannan fannin".
Ra'ayoyin sun taso ne bayan da bangarori daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka suka yi sanarwa da yawa game da AA, kodayake Amurka gabaɗaya ba ta da dabarun AI na hukuma.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta bayyana shirinta a bara, wanda shine ta zama babbar cibiyar fasaha ta wucin gadi a shekarar 2030.
"A ninka bincike na AI zai zama mai kyau farko, tun da sauran kasashen suna da nisa daga Amurka da kuma AI ne kawai neman na gaba nasara", Lee ya ce.
Biyu da kudade zai ninka chances na manyan AI binciken a Amurka, Lee ya shaida wa CNBC a wata hira da wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa mai suna "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" ya fito a wannan watan daga Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne Babban Daraktan Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya gudanar da bincike a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI na kasar Sin, Face ++.
A cikin shekarun 1980 a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya wuce mafi kyawun wasan kwaikwayo na Othello na Amurka kuma daga baya ya yi aiki a matsayin mai gudanarwa a Microsoft Research, kuma ya zama shugaban Google a yankin China.
Lee ya yaba da gasar fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka, ciki har da Hukumar Nazarin Ci gaban Ayyukan Tsaro ta Hukumar Nazarin Robotics, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a yi wani, don taimaka masa gano masu mafarki na gaba.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amurka sukan yi aiki tukuru don samun tallafin gwamnati.
"Ba wai kasar Sin ce ke jagorantar masana kimiyya ba, kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da wasu kamfanonin fasaha da dama sun dauki manyan jami'o'i da manyan mutane zuwa kungiyar AI a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce, sauya manufofin shige da fice zai taimaka wa Amurka ta inganta ayyukan AI.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba likitocin AA katin kore ta atomatik", in ji shi.
A watan Yulin 2017, Majalisar Jiha ta kasar Sin ta fitar da shirin bunkasa na gaba na AI.
