A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Ilimin Artificial Intelligence inda abokan hulɗa daga masana'antu da ilimi suka taru, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Ilimin Artificial.
Kuma a wannan watan, DARPA ta sanar da zuba jari na dala biliyan biyu a cikin wani shiri da ake kira AI NEXT.
