Yanzu kuma daga shafinmu na "Sunday Morning" 30 ga watan Satumba, 1882 shekaru 136 da suka gabata, kuma kafin ranar da aka tsara ... an haifi mai ilimin lissafi na gaba Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro hanyar ganowa da kuma auna radiyo: daga wannan kirkiro ya zo abin da ake kira Geiger counter.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an yi amfani da shi a matsayin ma'auni na kimiyya da kuma zama sanannen al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda a cikin fim din "Bells of Coronado" na 1950, wanda ke nuna Roy Rogers da Dale Evans, 'yan majalisa masu ban mamaki, ba su da masanin kimiyya:
Mutumin ya ce, "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan shi ne Geiger counter. Ana amfani da shi don gano ma'adanai masu rediyo, kamar uranium.
Idan ka sanya wadannan belun kunne, zaka iya jin tasirin atom a cikin ma'adanai".
Evans: "Haka ne, yana sauka a yanzu!"
