HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta bada rahoton karuwar sabbin masu dauke da cutar da kashi 14 cikin dari
Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS.
A yanzu haka, mutane sama da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a fadin kasar, a cewar hukumomin kiwon lafiya.
An samu karin mutane 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar a cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018.
Yawancin sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar suna da hanyar jima'i, wanda hakan ya nuna cewa ba za mu iya yin hakan ba.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu yankuna na kasar Sin ta hanyar karɓar jini mai cutarwa.
Amma wannan hanyar ta rage yawan mutanen da ke dauke da kwayar cutar HIV zuwa kusan sifili, kamar yadda jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin suka sanar a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, kowace shekara, yawan mutanen da ke fama da cutar HIV da AIDS a China na ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT a China.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT ya zama ruwan dare gama gari.
Saboda dabi'u masu ra'ayin mazan jiya a kasar nan, an kiyasta cewa bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin dari na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza sukan auri mace.
Yawancin cututtuka da ke kama da cututtuka suna faruwa ne ta hanyar jima'i ta hanyar rashin amfani da kariya.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar kanjamau ga kowa a kasar a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
