Wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web yana da burin kafa sabuwar hanyar Intanet da za ta yi gogayya da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web, yana son kaddamar da wani sabon kamfani da nufin yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya dogara da tsarin software na Open Source na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar wannan bayanin.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi dariya game da manufar da ke bayan Inrupt na "sarrafa duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar "kayan ajiyar bayanan sirri" ko POD.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalanda, ajiyar kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify: duk suna tare a cikin mai bincike guda, lokaci guda.
Wani abu na musamman na bayanan sirri na kan layi shine cewa ya dogara ne akan mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar wani nau'in bayani.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafa mutane ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar manajan darakta John Bruce, ra'ayin da ke bayan Inrupt shine: sanya albarkatu masu dacewa, matakai da ƙwarewa don taimakawa wajen sanya Solid aiki ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka da aka hayar su suyi aiki a kan aikin da kuma al'umma na masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar nasu aikace-aikacen rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke samuwa a shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da Facebook da Google game da bukatar yin canji na asali yayin da tsarin kasuwancin su ya canza gaba daya cikin dare.
"Ba mu tambayar su izinin su".
A cikin wani rubutu da aka buga a Medium a ranar Asabar Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da tsarin halittu da samar da wutar lantarki ta kasuwanci wanda zai taimaka kare mutuncin da ingancin sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da aka gina a Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, intanet ta sauya sosai lokacin da Berners-Lee ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da a lokacin da aka kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa mai kafa da kuma darektan Cibiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, Cibiyar Yanar Gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Buɗe.
"Ni mai matukar fata ne game da wannan zamani na gaba na Intanet", Berners-Lee ya kara da cewa.
Bernard Vann: An girmama limamin da Victoria Cross na yakin duniya na farko
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, limamin Ikilisiyar Ingila daya tilo da ya samu lambar yabo ta Victoria a matsayin jarumi a yakin duniya na farko, an ba shi lambar yabo a garinsu.
Mai daraja Lt. Colonel Bernard Vann ya samu lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga watan Satumbar 1918 a lokacin da aka kai farmaki a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Duk da haka, wani maharbi ya kashe shi kwanaki hudu bayan haka, kuma bai taba sanin cewa an ba shi lambar yabo mafi girma ta Birtaniya ba.
'Ya'yanta biyu sun nuna wani dutse a lokacin da ake gudanar da fareti a Rushden, Northamptonshire a ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce "abin alama ne ƙwarai" cewa an nuna dutsen bayan shekara 100 bayan ya ba kakansa kyautar.
A cewar jaridar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga watan Satumban 1918, Laftanar Kanar Vann ya jagoranci bataliyarsa a fadin tashar Saint-Quentin a cikin wani yanayi na "ƙuntatawa da kuma wuta mai tsauri daga bindigogi da bindigogi".
Sai ya yi sauri ya nufi layin farko na wuta, kuma da karfin hali ya jagoranci layin gaba har sai da ya sami bindiga da shi kadai ya harba a kan uku daga cikin filayen.
Wani dan bindiga ya kashe Lieutenant Colonel Vann a ranar 4 ga watan Oktoba na 1918, wata daya kafin a kawo karshen yakin.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce ya san ayyukan kakansa "ba zai taɓa iya yin su ba, amma hakan yana sa shi tawali'u".
Ita da ɗan'uwanta, Dr. James Vann, sun sanya wani adadi na furanni bayan bikin, wanda ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood ta jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce "ya kasance babban abin girmamawa a gare shi ya halarci faretin" ya kara da cewa "ya tabbatar da ƙarfin hali na ainihin jarumi da goyon bayan da mutane da yawa za su ba shi".
