Mickelson, wanda ba shi da kyau, ya zauna a kan kujera a gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa sabon tarihi a wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47 ranar Lahadi, amma zai bukaci ya kara karfi domin kada ya zama kamar ba shi da kyau.
Mickelson yana karya rikodin shekaru biyu yana wasa a karo na 12 a cikin wani abu guda; duk da haka, Jim Fury ya kori shi daga kujerar shugaban a ranar Asabar a cikin wasanni hudu da hudu.
Maimakon kasancewa a tsakiyar aikin, kamar yadda ya kasance sau da yawa ga Amurka, da biyar-lokaci babban zakara raba rana daga kasancewa wani cheerleader da kuma aiki a kan filin wasa, fatan gyara abin da ya sa shi wahala.
Bai taba kasancewa mai kai tsaye ba a cikin direbobi, ko da a lokacin da ya fi dacewa a cikin aikinsa, kuma mai shekaru 48 ba shine mafi kyawun zaɓi don tseren gasa na Le Golf National ba, inda 'yan wasa masu ƙarfi ke mamaye waɗanda suka rasa.
Kuma ko da yake filin wasa ba shi da ban tsoro, Mickelson, a wasa na tara, ranar Lahadi, zai fuskanci zakaran gasar British Open, Francesco Molina, wanda ya hada kai da rookie Tommy Fleetwood don cin nasara a wasanni hudu na wannan makon.
