Girgizar kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a. Jami'ai sun ce adadin wadanda suka mutu na iya tashi.
Saboda katsewar hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su iya samun bayanai daga gwamnatin Donggala ba, yankin da ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5, arewacin Palou.
Don Allah, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 tun bayan bala'in.
Ga muhimman bayanai game da garin Palu da kuma gwamnatin Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, kuma yana a ƙarshen wani kunkuntar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi; a cikin 2017, yana da mazaunan kusan 379,800.
A lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka auku, garin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala, a gefe guda, gwamnati ce da ke rufe yankin da ya fi kilomita 300 (180 miles) wanda ya ƙunshi gabar arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gwamnatin, wanda shine yankin gudanarwa wanda ke ƙarƙashin lardin, yana da mazaunan 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ya dogara ne da kamun kifi da noma, musamman a yankin gabar teku na Donggala.
Harkokin hakar ma'adinai na Nikela ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an mayar da hankali ne a Morowal, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Kasa ta Indonesia, Palu da Donggala sun sha wahala daga tsunami da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekara ta 1938, sama da mutane 200 suka mutu, kuma daruruwan gidaje sun lalace a cikin tsunami a Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996 wani tsunami ya sake afkawa a yammacin Donggala, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin girgizar ƙasa da ake kira 'Pacific Fire Belt' saboda haka ana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa.
Manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia, arewacin Sumatra, kuma ta haifar da tsunami.
2005: Daga karshen watan Maris zuwa farkon watan Afrilu, an samu girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar tekun yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java (tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia), kuma ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya girgiza gabar kudu, ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta afku a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta kudu.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afku a daya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta haifar da tsunami mai girman mita 10 wanda ya lalata garuruwa da dama, inda mutane kusan 300 suka mutu.
2016: An yi wata girgizar kasa a jihar Pidie Jaya a Aceh, wanda ya haifar da bala'i da tsoro, yayin da mutane suka tuna da lalacewar da girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004 suka haifar.
Babu wata guguwar tsunami a lokacin, amma mutane sama da 100 sun mutu lokacin da gine-ginen suka rushe.
2018: An yi wata babbar girgizar kasa a tsibirin Lombok da ke Indonesia, inda mutane sama da 500 suka mutu, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
