Game da ma'auni, matsakaici ne a cikin ko kusa da gundumar Pinellas, tsakanin low da high kusa da gundumar Hillsborough, babu kuma yayin da high a cikin Manatee County, babu kuma yayin da high kusa da gundumar Sarasota, babu kuma yayin da matsakaici a cikin gundumar Charlotte, babu kuma yayin da manyan kusa da gundumar Lee da low a cikin gundumar Collier.
Mutane da ke fama da haushi a numfashi na ci gaba da ƙaruwa a lardunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Amma babu wani irin wannan a cikin Arewa maso yammacin Florida a cikin makonni da suka gabata.
